        <h3 style="text-decoration: underline; text-align: center;">LIMITATIONS</h3>
        <apex:pageBlockSection >
            <b>All service providers should review their eXPRS Service Prior Authorizations to ensure they match the information contained in the Service Agreement. </b>
        	<p>
                In some instances, total units of service may be shared between multiple providers.
                In these instances, service providers and Persons Receiving Services/Employer are responsible
                for ensuring that the combined units of service among multiple providers do not exceed the maximum
                units available for the service. Services provided in excess of the maximum will not be paid.
            </p>
            <b>The maximum number of units listed in the eXPRS Service Prior Authorization
                {!Service_Assignment_Provider_JO__c.Units_shared_with_multiple_providers__c}
