                <li>All payments for services must be made through Express Payment and Reporting System (eXPRS).</li>
                <li>The Service Agreement is not a contract for payment. </li>
                <li>Mentor Oregon Brokerage is not responsible and will not make direct payments for any services in this agreement.</li>
                <li>The service provider is responsible for ensuring all his/her/its credentials are up to date as required and that the person receiving services is eligible to receive services.</li>
                <li>Provider must enter hours worked into eXPRS, and provide a completed timesheet or invoice to Mentor Oregon which describes service delivery.</li>
                <li>All payments for services follow the guidelines, schedules, and policies established by the State of Oregon and, if applicable, Collective Bargaining Agreement(s). </li>
            </ul>
            <b>**Invoices and timesheets that do not contain all required elements or those that
                are submitted more than 365 days past the date of service cannot be processed by Mentor Oregon Brokerage.**</b>
			<p>
                Billing documents requiring direct submission to Mentor Oregon Brokerage can be faxed, mailed or emailed to:
            </p>
